# What NOT to upload to Cloud Build for `gcloud run deploy --source .`.
# (Present → gcloud uses this instead of .gitignore.) Keep api/.sqlx and the
# Dockerfile; drop build artifacts, deps, secrets, and tooling cruft.
.git
.gitignore
**/target/
**/node_modules/
web/dist/
deploy/
**/*.env
!**/*.env.example
.playwright-mcp/
**/.DS_Store
